beer.beer_name: The World of Yesterday - Vienna Lager
beer.beer_description:
Freedom of roaming the world without
passport or visas, being confident that strangers are our brothers, that the world is open and full of promises. This is the Vienna from Stefan Zweig described in his 1942 novel "The world of yesterday". An elegant, generous and colorful Vienna. It was time to bring it back.
